graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks<br/>Workbench Images Component]

    %% External Dependencies (Required Infrastructure)
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>REQUIRED]
    Notebooks -->|CUDA images| CUDABase[CUDA Base Images<br/>quay.io/rhoai/cuda-*<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Notebooks -->|ROCm images| ROCmBase[ROCm Base Images<br/>quay.io/rhoai/rocm-*<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Notebooks -->|notebook UI| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4<br/>PyPI Package<br/>REQUIRED]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x<br/>PyPI Package<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x<br/>PyPI Package<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tool| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift CLI oc<br/>mirror.openshift.com<br/>REQUIRED]
    Notebooks -->|package manager| uv[uv 0.8.12<br/>PyPI Package<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Notebooks -.->|consumed by| NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Pod Lifecycle Mgmt]
    Notebooks -.->|listed by| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Workbench Selection UI]
    Notebooks -.->|used by| KubeflowPipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>Runtime Execution]
    Notebooks -.->|referenced by| ImageStreams[OpenShift ImageStreams<br/>Image References]

    %% External Services
    Notebooks -->|image storage| Quay[Quay.io Registry<br/>Container Registry<br/>REQUIRED]
    Notebooks -->|data access| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Object Storage<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Build Infrastructure
    Notebooks -->|built on| Konflux[Konflux CI/CD<br/>Build Platform<br/>REQUIRED]
    Notebooks -->|source code| GitHub[GitHub Repository<br/>red-hat-data-services/notebooks<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR]
    NotebookController -->|watches| NotebookCR
    NotebookController -->|creates pods using| Notebooks
    KubeflowPipelines -->|executes tasks using| Notebooks

    %% Styling
    style Notebooks fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies
    classDef externalRequired fill:#d9534f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef externalConditional fill:#f0ad4e,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef externalOptional fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    class UBI9,JupyterLab,OpenShiftCLI,uv,Quay,Konflux,GitHub externalRequired
    class CUDABase,ROCmBase,PyTorch,TensorFlow externalConditional
    class S3 externalOptional

    %% Internal ODH Components
    classDef internalODH fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    class NotebookController,Dashboard,KubeflowPipelines,ImageStreams,NotebookCR internalODH
